                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>to know who sent you the correspondence. Please, write<lb/> at once to the care of\n                    <hi rend=\"underline\">Prescott-House</hi>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">With <persName>Mrs. M's</persName> &amp; my best regard,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(5)\">I remain, in the greatest<lb/> haste</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">Yours</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">M Mayer</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p>The Sabbath-Sunday movement of this city<lb/> is <hi rend=\"underline\">exploded</hi>!\n                The society has <hi rend=\"underline\">dissolved</hi>! It<lb/> was a still-born\n                child.</p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
